contentrichtext.text: '''Otter Creek''' may refer to some places in the United States: ==Water bodies== * [[Otter Creek (British Columbia)]], a river in British Columbia * [[Otter Creek (Tennessee)]], a tributary of the Little Harpeth River * [[Otter Creek (Vermont)]], a tributary of Lake Champlain ** [[Otter Creek Brewing]] located in Middlebury, Vermont * [[Otter Creek (Georgia)]], a tributary of the [[Ocmulgee River]] ==Other uses== *[[Otter Creek, Florida]], a town *[[Otter Creek, Kentucky]] *[[Otter Creek, Eau Claire County, Wisconsin]], a town *[[Otter Creek, Dunn County, Wisconsin]], a town *[[Otter Creek, Minnesota]], an unincorporated community near Cloquet, Minnesota *[[Otter Creek Outdoor Recreation Area]] near Louisville, Kentucky *[[Otter Creek Township, LaSalle County, Illinois]], a township located near Streator, Illinois *[[Otter Creek Wilderness]], a wilderness area in West Virginia ==See also== *[[Otter Creek Township (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
